  <brief_title>Study to Assess Safety,Tolerability,Pharmacokinetics &amp; Antiviral Activity of JTK-853 in Hepatitis C Virus Genotype 1 Infected Subjects</brief_title>
  <official_title>Phase I,Randomized,Double-blind,Placebo-controlled,Multiple Dose Study Evaluating Safety,Tolerability,Pharmacokinetics and Antiviral Activity of JTK-853 in HCV Genotype 1 Infected Subjects,Followed by a Genotypic Resistance Monitoring Study</official_title>
  <sponsors>
