  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The purpose of this study was to determine the safety, tolerability, pharmacokinetics and
      anti-viral activity of JTK-853 in hepatitis C virus genotype 1 infected subjects based on
      reduction in viral load (HCV RNA level) from baseline to end of treatment, followed by
      genotypic resistance monitoring for up to one year after study drug treatment.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
